[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about serialization in the context of my config. So, it looks like only ObjArray can be serialized according to it. It makes me wonder why ObjToIntMap is able to serialize during testing but not in the actual config. Maybe there's a registration feature involved. I'm considering if I need to make UintMap serializable too. Also, I wonder if the existing ObjToIntMap is just missing from the config, or if the metadata has something to do with it.
